info: Rating, 4 stars,  路 April 2024,  路 Stayed one night
rating_comment:
its alright
I booked it for half a day as it was extremely hot outside, and I was close to IUB and the AC in IUB was not working as well as the wifi. I had an exam and needed internet connection. I needed a place to rest as well as charge my laptop to work on it. They have AC in the room and also power outlet for laptop and mobile and a cozy bed for few hours of rest. there is an attached toilet/shower which is helpful
good for short emergency stays

rating_comment: I always keep coming back to this place whenever I visit Dhaka and one thing for certain is that it never fails expectations. Overall Maati is the best, most budget-friendly, high-standard accommodations you can find in Dhaka in my opinion.

info: Rating, 4 stars,  路 January 2024,  路 Stayed about a week
rating_comment: It was a fairly good week long stay while I am searching for a new apartment in the neighborhood. The stay was peaceful, very responsive front desk people specially Ms. Anika who has provided me of cleaning support and amenities whenever needed. The room has a good TV, and kitchen amenities and private toilet/bath with hot water, which was helpful for me. The room has a balcony view at top floor and the noise level is very low so that is a plus for me. Overall good stay, close to Jamuna park and NSU/IUB universities.
